long_desc.thetext: The activity SPI should be enable extensions to provide a list of activity events for a particular scope. Initially providers would be registered programmatically but this would likely be implemented through an extension point in the future.

I have pushed a very simple provider implementation in addition to call back, IActivitySession, that enables providers to fire off events. I have also committed a proof of concept implementation for a TaskActivityProvider that returns related tasks based on references in the summary (related: bug 378101).
